Start with the Vite app shell, then build outward:

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    VITE[Vite app shell] --> API[routeApi.js]
    API --> HOOK[useRoutePoints]
    HOOK --> MAP[MapView]
    HOOK --> CONTROLS[RouteControls]
